# to-issues

Full workflow: `.claude/skills/to-issues/SKILL.md`.

Slice by outcome, not by layer (not "build all schemas" — instead "show transfer ratio on card detail"). Order by dependency. No issue tracker/GitHub remote is wired up yet, so output a checklist doc saved alongside the source PRD/decision, not real issues — confirm with the user before creating actual GitHub issues if a remote exists by the time this runs.
